features: BRUNO FROM DISNEY’S ENCANTO MOVIE: Inspired by Disney’s Encanto! Relive your favorite scenes and story moments!
SIGNATURE FASHION: Bruno’s outfit features authentic film details and designs.
ICONIC ACCESSORIES: Includes Bruno’s signature sandals!
AUTHENTIC HAIRSTYLE: Doll features Bruno’s curly hairstyle from the film for added play!

POSE AND PLAY: Doll is 11” tall, and articulated at the neck, shoulders, and hips, perfect for posing!.COLLECT THE MADRIGALS: Collect Bruno’s family members, Mirabel, Isabela, Luisa, and Dolores!.Includes: 1 Doll, 1 Doll Outfit, 1 Doll Poncho, 1 Pair of Doll Shoes.Suggested for Ages 3+ (small parts)

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 7, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars You can talk about Bruno.
reviews.reviewText: I was fortunate enough to pick this up on sale for 8 dollars, and it's a bargain. It's a perfect likeness of Bruno and about the size of a Barbie doll (bigger head though). The facial features and hair are accurate and the clothing is fine. I appreciated them getting the skin tone right--some of the other figures available through other stores made Bruno far too dark. He's a great addition to my Encanto collection.

reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars I talk about Bruno!
reviews.reviewText: Excellent likeness to the animated character. The head mold and his proportions overall look good. He is a basic doll with articulation only at the shoulders, hips and legs.
